These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, biathlon
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, zinnia
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, tiparillo
1. the bolivar-smoker is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
2. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Sport      | biathlon     | cycling      |
| Flower          | zinnia | sunflower    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Cigar   | bolivar  | tiparillo      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, green
2 different games are played: canasta, backgammon
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, zombie
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
3. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
4. the person watching mystery movies is not the person who likes green##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Color       | apricot         | green |
| Game         | backgammon | canasta   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery               | zombie  |

