.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, quad-bike
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
2 different games are played: bridge, domino
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, february
1. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Transport   | van       | quad-bike |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Game   | bridge | domino |
| Birthday           | january        | february   |

